<author>mạykl mnyr, wfyq ʿdly</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lytk thdyny qlbaⁿạ jdydaⁿạ
 qlbaⁿạ nqyaⁿ̃ạ wfyaⁿ̃ạ sʿyd
 lạ ẓlmẗ fyh ạ̉w kẖwfaⁿạ bl ḥbaⁿ̃ạ wfrḥaⁿạ wnwraⁿạ
 fryd
 qlbaⁿạ yḍyʾ bfyḍ ʿṭf qd sạl mn jnb ạlạbn
 ạlwḥyd
 ạlqrạr- nfsy fy ạsẖtyạq yạ dẖạ ạlbhạʾ
 tʿạl sryʿaⁿạ lạ tgẖfl ạlndạʾ
 ky yṣyr qlby ʿrsẖaⁿạ wsmạʾ
 2- hạ qlby rby byn ydyk qlbaⁿạ sẖqyaⁿ̃ạ ḥzynaⁿạ
 ʿnyd
 ạḥnu ʿlyh bnạẓryk fygẖdwạ lwḥaⁿạ lʿhd jdyd
 ạmktẖ fyh llạnqḍạʾ fygẖlw htạfy lrby ạlmjyd</lyrics>
